# UI/UX Six-Skill Stack (+ Higgsfield asset engine)

> **Asset layer — Higgsfield is MANDATORY.** Every raster/video/3D/audio asset a
> frontend needs is *generated* via Higgsfield (`mcp__higgsfield__*` /
> skill `higgsfield-generate`), never faked with placeholders, stock URLs, CSS-only
> gradients, or emoji-icons. The six craft skills below *arrange* those assets. Full
> capability→tool map + boundary: `rules/higgsfield-frontend-mandate.md`.

## Precedence (when rules conflict)

1. **Product truth** — Huashu #0 (WebSearch, PRODUCT.md) + Impeccable context gates
2. **Design tokens** — UI/UX Pro Max `--design-system` unless strict brand; designlang extracted > generated
3. **Assets (pixels)** — Higgsfield-generated for all image/video/3D/audio; no placeholder/stock survives to ship
4. **Layout/motion/copy** — Impeccable shared laws + absolute bans (DOM motion is code; its *media* is Higgsfield)
5. **Implementation** — Taste-Skill (React/Tailwind repos); advisory for other stacks
6. **Verification** — Huashu `verify.py` (HTML); Impeccable audit/critique/polish; confirm no faked asset remains

## Phases

| Phase | Actions |
|-------|---------|
| 0 — Source | `npx designlang <url>` for reference. `grade` for WCAG. `brand` for editorial guide. |
| A — Intake | Classify: marketing vs product, brand vs generic, constraints (a11y, dark mode, design system). |
| B — Context | Impeccable: `load-context.mjs`. UI/UX Pro Max: `search.py --design-system`. Taste-Skill: dials 8/6/4. |
| **Assets — Higgsfield** | For every image/video/3D/audio the design calls for: `models_explore(recommend)` → `generate_image`/`generate_video`/`generate_3d`/`generate_audio` → `upscale`/`reframe`/`remove_background`. NO placeholders/stock. (`higgsfield-generate`) |
| C — Build | Impeccable: `shape`→`craft`. Huashu: references router. Taste-Skill: enforce stack rules. Assemble Higgsfield assets; DOM motion references them. |
| D — Verify | Huashu: `verify.py`. Impeccable: audit/critique/polish. designlang: `grade`. Confirm no faked/placeholder asset shipped. |

